s":[22,23]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-ollama","ver":"2.0.7","Node name for S&R":"OllamaVision"},"widgets_values":["任务：仔细识别并读取图片内容，生成一段英文来描述图片\n\n要求：\n1. 角色与动作识别：请详细识别图片中的主要角色，包括人物、动物或其他实体，并准确描述它们的动作、姿态以及相互之间的关系\n2. 对话与文字解析：注意捕捉图片中的任何对话框、标签或文字信息\n3. 外观特征分析：观察并描述角色的外观特征，如颜色、形状、纹理等，同时分析画面的线条风格、笔触和色彩运用\n4. 背景与情感基调评估：对图片的背景进行简要描述，包括场景设置、环境元素等，并评估图片的整体情感基调，如欢快、沉重、神秘等\n5. 只输出内容本身，不带框定性描述语言\n6. 只输出英文","enable","http://127.0.0.1:11434","minicpm-v:8b",5,"text",193914508,"randomize"]},{"id":17,"type":"ShowText|pysssss","pos":[-1080,190],"size":[270,370],"flags":{},"order":3,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"text","localized_name":"text","name":"text","type":"STRING","link":23}],"outputs":[{"label":"STRING","localized_name":"字符串","name":"STRING","shape":6,"type":"STRING","links":null}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-custom-scripts","ver":"1.2.5","Node name for S&R":"ShowText|pysssss"},"widgets_values":["The image portrays a person with striking blonde hair styled in voluminous waves reminiscent of the 1940s era. The individual is adorned with elegant accessories, including pearl earrings and what appears to be a subtle neckpiece or choker.\n\nIn terms of attire, they wear an off-shoulder white dress that contributes to a classic yet glamorous aesthetic. Their makeup is meticulously applied, featuring bold red lipstick, well-defined eyebrows, and smoky eyeshadow, which enhances their expressive eyes with thick mascara.\n\nThe backdrop has a gradient from dark brown at the top transitioning into lighter shades towards the bottom right corner of the frame. This color scheme casts a warm glow on the subject's features, accentuating the golden tones in both hair and skin. The overall mood conveyed is one of vintage elegance and timeless beauty."]},{"id":18,"type":"ShowText|pysssss","pos":[-800,220],"size":[740,340],"flags":{},"order":4,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"text","localized_name":"text","name":"text","type":"STRING","link":24}],"outputs":[{"label":"STRING","localized_name":"字符串","name":"STRING","shape":6,"type":"STRING","links":null}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-custom-scripts","ver":"1.2.5","Node name for S&R":"ShowText|pysssss"},"widgets_values":["这幅画的主体是一位有着显眼的金色头发，造型如1940年代时期那样。该人物佩戴了优雅的配饰，包括珍珠耳环和看起来是轻微的颈饰或吊坠。\n\n衣服方面，他们穿着白色的斜肩礼服，这让人联想到经典却又高贵的气质。妆容精心地打理，口红为红色，眉毛清晰有形，眼影烟雾般，深使他们的眼睛显得更加迷人。用浓密的睫毛笔加上了一些遮瑕剂，让人觉得眼睛更具吸引力。\n\n背景采用渐变色，从上部开始逐渐变为底部右下角的较浅色，形成了温暖的光线照亮主体，将金发和皮肤中的黄色部分都突出了。整幅画的氛围是时尚典雅，美丽永恒。"]}],"links":[[22,15,0,16,1,"STRING"],[23,15,0,17,0,"STRING"],[24,16,0,18,0,"STRING"],[25,3,0,15,0,"IMAGE"]],"groups":[{"id":1,"title":"反推和翻译图片","bounding":[-1100,-400,1060,980],"color":"#3f789e","font_size":24,"flags":{}}],"config":{},"extra":{"ue_links":[],"links_added_by_ue":[],"ds":{"scale":0.9646149645000034,"offset":[1537.5497610242262,413.57354077628383]},"frontendVersion":"1.25.11","VHS_latentpreview":false,"VHS_latentpreviewrate":0,"VHS_MetadataImage":true,"VHS_KeepIntermediate":true},"version":0.4}